Package org.genthz

Interface GenerationProvider

public interface GenerationProvider
This class contains information for class instance generation such as InstanceBuilder, InstanceBuilder Filler and Selector.
Since:
3.0.0
Author:
mathter

  • Method Details

    • instanceBuilder

      <T> InstanceBuilder<T> instanceBuilder(InstanceContext context)
      Method returns appropriate InstanceBuilder for given context. Implementation of this method must search instance builder in this provider. If instance builder is not found the search must be continued in parent provider.
      Type Parameters:
      T - type of instance.
      Parameters:
      context - context.
      Returns:
      instance builder for instance creation.
      See Also:
      • up()

    • filler

      <T> Filler<T> filler(InstanceContext context)
      Method returns appropriate Filler for given context. Implementation of this method must search filler in this provider. If filler is not found the search must be continued in parent provider.
      Type Parameters:
      T - type of instance.
      Parameters:
      context - context.
      Returns:
      filler for instance filling.
